50:01.082 --> 50:03.000
<i>Call in the cavalry ♪</i>

50:03.084 --> 50:07.046
<i>Hey... ♪</i>

50:08.089 --> 50:11.008
<i>A taste of victory ♪</i>

50:11.092 --> 50:13.052
♪ ♪

50:16.097 --> 50:21.060
<i>♪ I'm gonna humor you
with the act of conversation</i> ♪

50:23.104 --> 50:27.066
<i>♪ I got my sunglasses on
from the sleep deprivation</i> ♪

50:29.110 --> 50:32.029
<i>♪ Should we drop you at home?
Are you waiting</i> ♪

50:32.113 --> 50:34.073
<i>For a last dance? ♪</i>

50:36.117 --> 50:39.036
<i>♪ You know you never got
the call 'cause I didn't want</i> ♪

50:39.120 --> 50:40.288
<i>The romance ♪</i>

